<div class="hero-trainer">
  <div class="card-trip bg-black">
    <%= image_tag 'home-page.png', style: 'max-width: auto; height: 79vh;' %>
    <div class="bg-black">
      <div>
        <h4 class="fw-bold text-white text-center">Hero Trainer is a platform that connects users with elite training partners <br>
          for personalized workouts and skill development</h4>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div>
    <div class="text-center mt-4">
      <h3><b>Explore popular trainer</b></h3>
    </div>
    <%= render "slider", locals: {users: @users }  %>
    <div class="container mt-4 text-center">
      <%= link_to "Browse Lessons", lessons_path, class: "btn btn-dark" %>
    </div>
    <div class="container d-flex my-5">
      <div class="col-md-6 d-flex">
        <%= image_tag 'gym.png', class: 'w-100' %>
      </div>
      <div class="row col-md-6 mx-5">
        <div class="d-flex my-2">
          <div>
            <%= image_tag 'flow1.png', class: 'me-4',style: 'max-width: 70px; height: auto;'%>
          </div>
          <div >
            <h5><b>① At any time</b></h5>
            <p>Please come at any time during business hours. Once you have put your belongings away and changed your clothes, you can use the available space to warm up.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex my-2">
          <div>
            <%= image_tag 'flow2.png', class: 'me-4', style: 'max-width: 70px; height: auto;'%>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h5><b>②Select the start time</b></h5>
            <p>Choose an available round to start your workout. Check the coaching screen to see what kind of exercise you'll be doing and get ready.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex my-2">
          <div>
            <%= image_tag 'flow3.png', class: 'me-4', style: 'max-width: 70px; height: auto;'%>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h5><b>③Start your workout</b></h5>
            <p>Boxing round: punching the punching bag / pad punching. <br>
              Strength round: training to improve physical function</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex my-2">
          <div>
            <%= image_tag 'flow4.png', class: 'me-4', style: 'max-width: 70px; height: auto;' %>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h5><b>4. Finish your workout with a fist bump</b></h5>
            <p>Once you've completed your workout, enjoy the endorphins rush.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container mt-5">
      <div class="row text-center">
        <div class="col-md-4 d-flex flex-column">
          <p class="fw-bold">Work out as soon as you get to the location</p>
          <p>The appeal of Hero Trainer is that you can book a trainer whenever you want and start your workout whenever you want.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 d-flex flex-column">
          <p class="fw-bold">A new workout every day</p>
          <p>A unique training workout. A new workout every day, so you'll never get bored!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 d-flex flex-column">
          <p class="fw-bold">Private lessons and group workouts</p>
          <p>Our trainers will provide individualized instruction for each member. With one-on-one help with form correction and performance, it's a comfortable workout that's suitable for everyone!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center my-5">
      <h4 class="fw-bold">Social Media</h4>
      <p>We post new information about Hero Trainer on social media. Please follow us.</p>
      <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
        <a href="https://www.facebook.com/" target="_blank">
          <%= image_tag 'fb-logo.png', style: 'max-width: 30px; height: auto;', class: 'mx-2' %>
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/" target="_blank">
          <%= image_tag 'ig-logo.png', style: 'max-width: 30px; height: auto;', class: 'mx-2'  %>
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.x.com/" target="_blank">
          <%= image_tag 'x-logo.png', style: 'max-width: 30px; height: auto;', class: 'mx-2'  %>
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/" target="_blank">
          <%= image_tag 'yt-logo.png', style: 'max-width: 30px; height: auto;', class: 'mx-2'  %>
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.line.me/en/" target="_blank">
          <%= image_tag 'line-logo.png', style: 'max-width: 30px; height: auto;', class: 'mx-2'  %>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <%= render "slider-mini" %>
    <div class="card bg-black text-white">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row text-center my-5">
          <div class="col-md-5 text-start">
            <h4 class="fw-bold">Hero Trainer</h4>
            <p>HT JAPAN Co., Ltd.</p>
            <p>Shibuya Building 1F, 1-3-11 Udagawacho, Shibuya, Tokyo</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-2 d-flex flex-column text-start">
            <p class="fw-bold">Menu</p>
            <p>HOME</p>
            <p>ABOUT</p>
            <p>WORKOUT</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-2 d-flex flex-column text-start">
            <p class="fw-bold">ANY</p>
            <p>MEDIA</p>
            <p>CONTACT US</p>
            <p>COMPANY</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-3 d-flex flex-column text-start">
            <p class="fw-bold">Privary & Legal</p>
            <p>Privacy Policy and Personal Information</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
